high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the potato on the cutting board over the sink.
Move left to the counter left of the sink.
Slice the tomato that is on the counter.
Carry the knife to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back to the sliced tomato.
Take a slice of the tomato.
Carry the tomato slice to the microwave above the sink on your right.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave.
Take the tomato slice back to the counter left of the sink.
Place the tomato slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the potato.
Move slightly to the left to stand in front of the tomato on the counter.
Cut half the tomato into slices.
Move slightly to the right to stand in front of the sink.
Toss the knife into the sink, putting it on the left hand side of the apple.
Move slightly to the left to stand in front of the tomato on the counter.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Move slightly to the right to stand in front of the sink.
Above the sink, open the microwave door.  Put the tomato slice in front of the mug, close the door, and microwave the slice for a few seconds.  Take out the tomato slice and close the door.
Move slightly to the left to stand in front of the tomato and coffee maker on the counter.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato slice on the counter near the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that's near the potato.
Move slightly to your left.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Move over to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife into the right side of the sink.
Move back over to the tomato.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Move to the middle of the sink and look up.
Cook the tomato in the fridge and then get it back out and close the door.
Move about a foot to the left of where you cut up the tomato facing the coffee maker.
Put the tomato in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Take a step to the left and face the counter with a tomato on it.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Take a step to the right and face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a step to the left and face the counter with a tomato on it.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Take a step to the right and face the microwave above the sink.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the left and face the counter with a tomato on it.
Put the tomato slice on the counter on the left of the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: TO cut a tomato as well as heat a slice of the tomato.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the dish-drying area to the left of the sink.
Move left to the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Move right to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move left to the counter.
Pick up tomato slice from the counter.
Turn right, turn left to face counter and microwave again.
Put tomato in the microwave and cook it, take tomato out of microwave..
Turn away from counter, turn back to face counter.
Put the slice of tomato on the font of the counter to the right of the espresso machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on the counter.
